INSERT INTO `ss_cms_article` VALUES ('25', '79', '77', '0,77,', null, null, null, '究竟客厅墙面贴砖好不好 墙面砖品牌有哪些', 'zhuangxun-jiu-jing-ke-ting-qiang-mian1', '#FF0000', 'bold', '推荐,还看,相关', '测试来源01：http://baijia.baidu.com', 'admin', '', '', '', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">装修客厅时，如果在客厅墙面贴上墙面砖的话，那么就会让客厅变得非常高大上，而且还会让客厅比较的光亮，但究竟<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit;\">客厅墙面贴砖好不好</span>?还是有很多朋友想要知道答案，既然这样，那么装修之家小编就带着大家来了解一下，究竟客厅墙面贴砖好不好以及墙面砖品牌有哪些?</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://img01.lingdangpet.cn/cms-images/article/2019_01_04/c0519bcad617c81f9570f256c4b1c4bb.jpg\" title=\"客厅墙面贴砖好不好\" alt=\"客厅墙面贴砖好不好\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">一、究竟客厅墙面贴砖好不好</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">1、在装修客厅时，如果贴上墙面砖的话，不但是非常好看，而且装修效果也是会非常好的，所以就深受消费者的喜欢，但我们也是要选择对墙面砖颜色的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">2、如果贴上墙面砖的话，还有一个很大的优点，那就是比较地实用，就比如说是在打扫地时候吧，就比较容易，只要用抹布轻轻一擦就可以了，所以说就省下了我们很多打扫的时间。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51