INSERT INTO `ss_cms_photo` VALUES ('28', '76', '84', '0,84,', null, null, null, '楼梯效果图，复式建筑楼梯装修的类型', 'shi-jian-zhu-lou-ti-zhuang-xiu-de-lei-xing', '', '', '推荐', '', 'admin', '', '', '', '<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">在进行复式建筑装修的时候，它的楼梯装修是重要的一部分。在装修楼梯的时候会有很多楼梯的类型，那么，什么种类的楼梯装饰性更强呢？在进行楼梯装修的时候有什么注意事项？<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 12px;\">接下来就请大家跟随装修之家小编一起来了解一下有关</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit;\">楼梯效果图</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 12px;\">的一些内容吧。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"楼梯效果图\" alt=\"楼梯效果图\" src=\"http://img01.lingdangpet.cn/cms-images/photo/2019_01_04/3a5b56b8faa035e4decd071b2c986888.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">楼梯效果图-----复式楼梯的装修类型</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">a、直梯：这种类型的楼梯是比较传统的类型，但现在却是罕见的，因为它占用了更多的空间。如果它是一个小型的复式建筑，只要简化直梯，就不是那么多空间了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">b、弧形楼梯：弯曲形状更适合大型复式房屋。如果它是一个小型复式房，它不仅昂贵，而且还有利可图。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">Ç、梯子：这是最现代的复式房源会选择，因为坡度不一样大，直楼梯和梯子折叠梯可以充分利用的设计。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">设计为一个存储空间，可以容纳大量的碎片在家里，作出合理的利用空间，并确保清洁和秩序在家里。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">d、旋转梯：这种类型的楼梯是折叠梯的变体，但覆盖区是不一样大的楼梯，并且通常用装饰材料如锻铁玻璃、，这是相当美观。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">楼梯效果图-----复式楼梯如何设计更合理</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">a、楼梯坡度</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">楼梯的坡度与缩放攀爬效率、的舒适度和空间状态等有关。然而，家用梯子的倾斜度通常为20°-45°，优选为约30°。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">b、踏板设计</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">这是合理的梯脚的宽度比人的鞋的尺寸稍大，此外，阶梯的两个步骤之间的高度为12毫米，因为高度是最佳的，当你走在它。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">c、楼梯栏杆</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">扶手也是复式建筑楼梯的重要组成部分，尤其是家中老人的极端需求。但是，当它是个性化的时候，有足够的空间可供选择。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"楼梯效果图\" alt=\"楼梯效果图\" src=\"http://img01.lingdangpet.cn/cms-images/photo/2019_01_04/cb90c816e8a3b3c532bc7663c5a28af3.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">木制扶手将更柔软，更舒适，而锻铁具有强烈的复古触感，但冬天更冷。观察每个所有者的偏好和需求，但是您想要保证哪个并不重要。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">d、选择扶手</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">栏杆与楼梯结合的稳定性也是楼梯的安全的一个重要方面。风格是大约栏杆和扶手和楼梯的组合是非常重要的。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">楼梯效果图-----复式建筑楼梯<a href=\"https://www.zxzhijia.com/Info/zhishi/69402.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; outline: none; color: rgb(51, 179, 113); transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; text-decoration-line: none;\">装修的注意事项</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">1、梯形的主要功能是连接上部和下部空间，允许人们安全地从一侧走到另一侧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">只有满足这些需求，我们才能开始考虑美学以及它是否能吸引人们的注意力。安装梯子就像修理负载墙一样。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">这是一个非常重要的项目。确保楼梯的位置正确。否则，如果你回去工作会有问题。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">2、梯形包括直线、L形式、C形式、U形式、S旋转形式，因此在安装楼梯时必须考虑以下因素。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">内部楼梯的坡度一般为20至45度，最佳坡度约为30度。楼梯的两个水平结构之间的垂直空间需要至少2米。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">楼梯的台阶尺寸适合于人脚的台阶尺寸，并且行走时感觉舒适的台阶通常小而宽。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">普通混凝土基座具有大约16厘米的舒适高度，梯子的宽度通常由销的流动确定，以确保平稳通过。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">3、楼梯材料。木制楼梯给人一种慷慨的感觉很温暖，房子的装饰风格也更容易协调。金属梯子相对较强，但总体感觉相对较冷，使用时会感觉更冷，有时不符合家庭的整体装饰风格。楼梯效果图</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img title=\"楼梯效果图\" alt=\"楼梯效果图\" src=\"http://img01.lingdangpet.cn/cms-images/photo/2019_01_04/9fcc723ba708e85182b5a4d34f8b3adb.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">另一个问题是如果处理不好，楼梯的角落容易发生碰撞。玻璃楼梯的好处在于视觉上的敏感和轻盈。然而，玻璃梯更昂贵，因为它需要使用具有良好承载能力的钢化玻璃。楼梯效果图</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; box-sizing: inherit; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;\">以上就是小编今天为你整理的有关楼梯效果图的一些内容，楼梯的装修不光要考虑楼梯的外观美观度还要考虑安全性，大家在装修之前下了解一些装修知识是有必要的。希望上面的内容能够对有需要的朋友带来一点帮助，感谢您的阅读，想要了解更多资讯请继续关注装修之家网。</p><p><br/></p>', 'cms-images/photo/2019_01_10/eb21014b7fdddf0ff25dd46a62c15e9e==1500x1125.jpg', '', '4', '4', '1546531200', '0', '0', '0', 'zh-CN', '1546591782', '1553442059');
